title: Hour 2 - Chiefs Offense Looks Good, Mark Sanchez

description:
Dan thinks the Chiefs offense looked good last night and talks to former NFL QB, Mark Sanchez about how the loss of Tyreek Hill may have actually improved the Chiefs' offensive scheme.
